# MacOS Dotfiles

### Quick Run

```bash
sh -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/schalk-conradie/dotfiles/main/install.sh)"
```

### Included

- Ghostty (terminal emulator)
- Git configuration
- Home directory settings
- Neovim configuration
- Starship prompt
- Tmux configuration
- Yazi file manager
- Zsh configuration